{"tid":2443393,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"官涌體育館續有市民打針 女保安：我哋大陸㗎嘛！","createTime":"2021-03-12T04:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T09:13:54.000Z","uid":130626,"like":176,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"998dbc495ea0f97427eb71971646b74f3db38a7b","tid":2443393,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:48:18.000Z","msg":"今早記者到官涌體育館疫苗接種中心視察，出入的人流比較疏落，不過有接種疫苗後離開的市民指，體育館內有約100人，尚幸等候時間不算太長。<br />\n<br />\n陳小姐做保安，是新增優先組別之一。她表示並非公司要求，而是個認為須要接種疫苗。至於何以選擇「科興」，她表示對它有信心：「因為我哋大陸㗎嘛、中國㗎嘛！」<br />\n<br />\n另一位市民譚女士（67歲）聲言對中國疫苗有信心，認為接種「科興」後的死亡個案是個別事件，她說：「係嗰個人身體狀況有問題。」所以她不考慮其他疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n另一位接種疫苗的李先生從事運輸業，屬於新增優先組別之中的公共交通從業員之一。他表示對「科興」不擔心：「擔心咩啫，本身無病無毒。」<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210312/B5FMVPTX4BGBFFEGCAITXOTXUI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210312%2FB5FMVPTX4BGBFFEGCAITXOTXUI%2F&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw7ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=368b8ebf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210312%2FB5FMVPTX4BGBFFEGCAITXOTXUI%2F&h=141e67c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210312/B5FMVPTX4BGBFFEGCAITXOTXUI/</a>"},{"pid":"d1b31e79684f6edcc393b913d76ada305f296888","tid":2443393,"uid":221343,"like":284,"dislike":1,"score":283,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:49:47.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎都係來自大陸,咁你又驚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283e015d42dcaddf9d51e805474a04500d325960","tid":2443393,"uid":242537,"like":141,"dislike":0,"score":141,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:50:26.000Z","msg":"屌 咩 邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：至於何以選擇「科興」，她表示對它有信心：「因為我哋大陸㗎嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><